Package: WordsChars
Title: Counts characters and words on a string
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Juan", "Burckhardt", , "jburckha@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows you to count the number of characters and words in a given string.
    You can also decide weather you want to count spaces as character or not. When given a string, you will
    get a vector in return whose first element is the number of characters and second element is the number of words.
